      "content": "that makes sense. i have a client who's a female executive, high level stuff. she was asking about hair specifically. she has a lot of natural texture/coils and prefers not to use heat or chemicals to straighten it out. what kind of advice would you give her to make sure her hair still fits that \"neatly combed and styled\" professional look you mentioned?",
